{"tid":1692691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點解d popo咁緊張要去了解墮樓科大生既傷勢","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:07:38.000Z","uid":289751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92423567c9028c7f78f663b0e4fba18e0c61d692","tid":1692691,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"尋晚入院已經知道佢傷勢好嚴重<br />\n班popo晏就走去了解傷勢咁熱心???<br />\n口講話科大生避催淚彈墮樓<br />\n有無直播?有無人見到?一開頭係邊嗰講避催淚彈?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">停車場一定有cctv同車cam<br />\n一定要搵返當時段片證明發6生咩事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n懷疑在將軍澳躲避催淚彈期間、由尚德邨停車場墮下的科大學生，繼續在伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部留醫，情況危殆。下午一時許，兩名東九龍總區警員到醫院，嘗試了解墮樓學生的傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n兩名警員逗留約20分鐘，確認傷者在病房接受治療後離開。警員引述醫護人員說，傷者現在不適合會面。警員又說，暫時只知道傷者墮下跌傷，未打算有拘捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名學生腦出血，早上完成腦部手術，多名親友到醫院探望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489983-20191104.htm?fbclid=IwAR1xHsXhpPVUPukiQmh2kKMliE4UuT-90zy3IhEQq4QJPz2kyhE6up1yGbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489983-20191104.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xHsXhpPVUPukiQmh2kKMliE4UuT-90zy3IhEQq4QJPz2kyhE6up1yGbY&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=90fe464d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489983-20191104.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xHsXhpPVUPukiQmh2kKMliE4UuT-90zy3IhEQq4QJPz2kyhE6up1yGbY&h=cf334c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489983-20191104.htm?fbclid=IwAR1xHsXhpPVUPukiQmh2kKMliE4UuT-90zy3IhEQq4QJPz2kyhE6up1yGbY</a>"},{"pid":"1af26999cfe42bd32884bc036fde822580ab6c0a","tid":1692691,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"有無人住個到?<br />\n邊個係區議員?<br />\n停車場管理處係邊個?"},{"pid":"559017db4a2d433ed2edabeac951c8adcc171395","tid":1692691,"uid":304269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"醒咗要錄口供，對佢地係不利"},{"pid":"9f765bc6e176ea85da338b367d7cfee3f75a17a9","tid":1692691,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"宜家嗰個區議員係工聯會既簡兆祺, 可以收皮<br />\n但係黎緊邊個去選?"}]}